{
  "stem": "393.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Something, such thing happened, maybe we think maybe, maybe we did something wrong, or who knows?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a lot of praying that time, but looks like sometimes God is also distracted.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the railroad station, we were-- the doors were open.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They did the, the-- what do you call the-- those trains?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they called them the freight trains.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Freight trains.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were pushed in, as many as they could.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was also-- because we, we, we didn't expect that yet.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You see, if you-- if you don't live through such things, you can't imagine that such a thing could happen.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You are dazed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You are confused.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What's going on here?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What's happening here?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Oh, one after another.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Fast, fast.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "One after another.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But 18 freight.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's a known thing by now, you see?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We couldn't stretch our limbs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We didn't have room.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We didn't have air.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] One pail of water, and one-- the other pail for the toilet purposes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Man, woman, religious people, you know, children, all-- everything together over there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everyrhing, everybody express themselves the way they could, you know, by praying, by cursing, by yelling , by crying.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All kind of things.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, that freight, that three days till Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like just unhuman.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Just you-- just-- even now, even I lived that through, it's, it's hard for me to, to-- how could such thing-- how could they make such thing, you know?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we, we put our sheet around us and we changed, or we did whatever we had to do.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we went one by one to the window to catch a little air.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There's a small, little window with rails.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Sometimes we are very strong.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Sometimes we just can't endure.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
